  "summary": "The trick to bags of flavour in this chilli is blackening the onion and garlic for the chipotle sauce. It adds a smoky depth which complements the chipotle. Ideal for batch cooking, you could even double the quantities of this chipotle chilli con carne and then keep portions in the freezer - ideal for when you need an instant Mexican-inspired meal to hand. If you enjoy cooking with spice, you’re going to really get a kick out of the flavours in this simple chilli.",
